"ali Farka Toure" iga yan uxatar azentar g [[Azawan|uzawan]] n [[Tafriqt]] d tanzruft. ymmut g taddart nes g Mali dart yan imenghi agezzaf d tmadunt.Ali ilul g Kanau iqqimen degs yessker takat d imurig nes allig yuley ig itri g ignwan n uzawan amadlan. ssent kullu middn s isnagaren nns d id ifilun n Blues. Ali ayd asen yennan : " uridd ghas g yan imi ag thellaw tamimy" . Lligh d da isawal xef Toumani Dyabet, amedyaz d ugriot axatar yanna " Toumani iga anazur s tidt" amid is netta iga ghas yan umezzan. Ali yannsem wida yessken Blues ur issen mayd iga neck essnegh tiqsisin, amzruy tamitlojit n unarat eddegh.
Ali yessufeghd asggas eddegh album nes G ul n wayyur ( In the Heart of the Moon) yamez ghifs digh yan ugafay seg Gramy Awards.
Imec alligh iga asaru i ugdud n uzawan anzezruf g Mali 2003. ntta d Oumou Sangare, d Inariwen d Blackfire, yerzemd ihellalen i wiyyad ad digh sefden imeccehcuten i ijwawaden n tnezraf ad nisil.
Ali ad teswunfud g umalu n ubda.
